Package: allowayai
Type: Package
Title: Sports Analytics and Machine Learning Toolkit
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-03-14
Authors@R: person("Ian", "Alloway", email = "ianalloway@usf.edu",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: A toolkit for sports analytics and machine learning workflows.
    Provides functions for converting betting odds to implied probabilities,
    calculating Kelly Criterion bet sizing, evaluating model edge distributions,
    and tracking model performance over time. Implements both S3 and S4 class
    systems for structured analytics objects. Includes utilities for data frame
    type inspection and bankroll simulation.
