Package: allowayai
Type: Package
Title: AI and Sports Analytics Utility Toolkit
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-03-14
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Ian",
    family = "Alloway",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "ian@ianalloway.xyz",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")
  )
Description: A collection of utility functions for data science, sports analytics,
    and machine learning workflows. Includes tools for fractional Kelly Criterion
    bet sizing, S3/S4 object-oriented model tracking, edge visualization, implied
    probability conversion, and data frame type inspection. Designed for analysts
    who build predictive models for sports betting markets and need clean,
    reproducible tools for both research and production use.
